{"tid":1593481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再出假標題既post啦好嗎","createTime":"2019-09-25T05:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T06:08:14.000Z","uid":11798,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb00a5e1bcbd29ab7c7fa3ec316aa988a3dc0a6f","tid":1593481,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"而家連登超過90%標題post只有一個目的 就係叫人推post <br />\n<br />\n你咁得閑諗點fake人入來又要打咁多字 出post叫大家推post 不如將名已留既post 幫手推一推好過啦<br />\n<br />\n成個吹水台三日唔埋兩日就假標題post 叫人推 <br />\n有無諗過你地D標題post（目的一樣）充斥住全個吹水台 有時班5毛得閑又洗返曬上來 大家又善忘唔用不推文覆標題post<br />\n<br />\n標題post 充斥吹水台 舊post/ 其他就會沉<br />\n你每出一個假標題post 連登就少一行俾人見到要推既post<br />\n搞到大家誤會無人推<br />\n來手成班標題黨又衝出來<br />\n大佬呀惡性循環來架 唔好再出假標題post啦<br />\n好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好試開fake post 試下直接推post"},{"pid":"9aed0f9a6780065d6e18f56a14375f14ed52b728","tid":1593481,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"c5df42de698bd2170ec11c3444734cc162525871","tid":1593481,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:50:25.000Z","msg":"而家見到標題撚，就算入面打得幾好都唔會幫佢推，因為個標題好趕客<br />\n<br />\n唔該唔好再做標題撚啦，有時想上黎推行動戰略post真係唔會入去睇架"},{"pid":"a8dfdf1d262a8cb9eb4dfad96e5471dbcd5e6f26","tid":1593481,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:02:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f5795126ecc7257a1c896be0a43709b90387021e","tid":1593481,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:08:14.000Z